VALUES(10397, 7, '2020-12-30 15:28:41', '2020-12-30 15:28:41', '<h2>Where Students Unite!</h2>
<h3>Connect</h3>
<h3>Collaborate</h3>
<h3>Communicate</h3>
<img src="/wp-content/themes/peepso-theme-gecko/assets/images/Landing-image.png" />
        <h3>What is Dojoko?</h3>
        <p>
              Dojoko is an AI-powered global eco-system focused on the needs of students and young professionals. Our aim is to help the younger generation build a global network of like-minded supporters, identify academic and career opportunities that meet individual needs.
2020 has been a challenging year. In a time of separation, Dojoko brings people together to help them connect, collaborate and communicate with each other. Anyone of any background, location or nationality is welcome here. 
        </p>
        <h3>Why Create Dojoko?</h3>
        <p>
              Did you know up to 70% of students don’t find a job in their field of study and that the younger generation is 3 times more likely to be unemployed! The system has not changed in decades (maybe even centuries). Get a degree. Find a job. Conform to the standards set by the older generation. It is time for change!Students are the future leaders and yet not a single platform exists to empower them! Dojoko has been created to EMPOWER our younger generation to connect, collaborate and communicate with each other so that they can decide the world they want to live in.
        </p>
        <h3>Our Team</h3>
        <img src="/wp-content/themes/peepso-theme-gecko/assets/images/Artboard%20–%201.svg" />
        <p>
              The founders are business, finance, technology and humanity enthusiasts. Majority of our team comprise students and young professionals from diverse countries, cultures and backgrounds.
        </p>', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2021-01-09 10:27:33', '2021-01-09 10:27:33', '', 0, 'https://dojoko.com/?page_id=10397', 0, 'page', '', 0);


